<li><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20.3999996185303px;">S &ndash; спотовая цена акции, </span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20.3999996185303px;">r &ndash; ставка без риска, </span></li>
